==== Chapter 14: The Mineral Work

#doctrine[
  "Know that all the seven metals are born from a threefold matter, namely, Mercury, Sulphur, and Salt, but with distinct and peculiar colorings.... Mercury is the Spirit, Sulphur is the Soul, and Salt is the body." — Paracelsus
